About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues which are socially relevant.The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son pushes Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues which are socially relevant.The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son pushes Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

title: Nidahas Trophy 2018 Final: Highlights from India (IND) vs Bangladesh (BAN)
tags: dinesh karthik|"dinesh karthik six"|"India vs Bangladesh"|"Nidahas trophy 2018"|"Sri Lanka Independence Cup"|"IND vs BAN"|"#INDvBAN"|"MS Dhoni six"|"rohit sharma"|"KKR"|"IPL 2018"|"PSL 2018"|"soumya sarkar"|"nagin dance"|"shakib al hasan"|"mustafizur rahman"|"washington sundar"|"chahal"|"shikhar dhawan"|"vijay shankar"|"KL Rahul"|"India T20 win"
description: In one of the most exciting T20 matches, India won the Nidahas Trophy 2018 courtesy Dinesh Karthik's heroics. With India being set a target of 167, it looked India's game to lose at the halfway. In one of the rare failures of the series, Shikhar Dhawan wasn't able to provide the start to India as he has. But Rohit Sharma made sure that India was cruising at the halfway mark of 10 overs. Once he got out, Manish Pandey and Vijay Shankar tried to take India forward. With the 18th over of Mustafizur Rahman giving away just 1 run and getting Pandey's wicket, it looked Bangladesh's game to lose. But in the penultimate over, Karthik smashed 22 runs making sure India needed 12 runs of the last over. With Soumya Sarkar bowling at full length most deliveries Shankar perished. India still needed 5 runs of the last ball. What transpired after this was a six by Dinesh Karthik in making sure that India still remains unbeaten against Bangladesh in T20I.

title: ‡§ï‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§Ü‡§™ ‡§á‡§∏ ‡§ú‡§ó‡§π ‡§™‡§∞ ‡§â‡•ú ‡§∏‡§ï‡§§‡•á ‡§π‡•ã ? | 3 Places Where Gravity Does Not Seem to Exist
tags: top 5|"top 10"|"gravity"|"science videos"|"places on earth without gravity"|"places on earth where gravity fails"|"anti gravity places on earth"|"anti gravity"|"levitation"|"levitation magic"|"earth"|"magnetic hill"|"zero gravity"
description:
Gravity, or gravitation, is a natural phenomenon by which all things with mass are brought toward (or gravitate toward) one another, including objects ranging from atoms and photons, to planets and stars. Since energy and mass are equivalent, all forms of energy (including light) cause gravitation and are under the influence of it.

Levitation is the process by which an object is held aloft, without mechanical support, in a stable position.

Levitation is accomplished by providing an upward force that counteracts the pull of gravity (in relation to gravity on earth) , plus a smaller stabilizing force that pushes the object toward a home position whenever it is a small distance away from that home position. The force can be a fundamental force such as magnetic or electrostatic, or it can be a reactive force such as optical, buoyant, aerodynamic, or hydrodynamic.

Anti-gravity also known as non-gravitational field is an idea of creating a place or object that is free from the force of gravity. It does not refer to the lack of weight under gravity experienced in free fall or orbit, or to balancing the force of gravity with some other force, such as electromagnetism or aerodynamic lift. Anti-gravity is a recurring concept in science fiction, particularly in the context of spacecraft propulsion.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues which are socially relevant.The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son pushes Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

description: Watch the new trailer for #Mowgli starring Christian Bale, Cate Blanchett, Benedict Cumberbatch, and Freida Pinto. Only in theaters October 19.--Motion capture and live action are blended for ‚ÄúMowgli,‚Äù a new, big-screen, 3D adaptation of Rudyard Kipling‚Äôs classic The Jungle Book.  The film features an impressive roster of stars under the direction of Andy Serkis.The story follows the upbringing of the human child Mowgli, raised by a wolf pack in the jungles of India.  As he learns the often harsh rules of the jungle, under the tutelage of a bear named Baloo and a panther named Bagheera, Mowgli becomes accepted by the animals of the jungle as one of their own.  All but one: the fearsome tiger Shere Khan.  But there may be greater dangers lurking in the jungle, as Mowgli comes face to face with his human origins.The actors performing the roles of the story‚Äôs central animal characters are: Oscar winner Christian Bale (‚ÄúThe Fighter,‚Äù the ‚ÄúDark Knight‚Äù Trilogy) as the cunning panther, Bagheera; Oscar winner Cate Blanchett (‚ÄúBlue Jasmine,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Aviator‚Äù) as the sinister snake, Kaa; Oscar nominee Benedict Cumberbatch (‚ÄúThe Imitation Game,‚Äù ‚ÄúAvengers: Infinity War‚Äù) as the fearsome tiger, Shere Khan; Oscar nominee Naomie Harris (‚ÄúMoonlight,‚Äù ‚ÄúSkyfall‚Äù) as Nisha, the female wolf, who adopts the baby Mowgli as one of her cubs; and Andy Serkis (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù trilogy, ‚ÄúStar Wars: The Last Jedi‚Äù) as the wise bear, Baloo.  On the human side, Matthew Rhys (‚ÄúThe Post‚Äù) is Lockwood; Freida Pinto (‚ÄúKnight of Cups‚Äù) is Messua; and young actor Rohan Chand (‚ÄúThe Hundred-Foot Journey,‚Äù ‚ÄúBad Words‚Äù) will play Mowgli, the boy raised by wolves.Rounding out the cast are Peter Mullan (‚ÄúTommy‚Äôs Honour‚Äù), as the leader of the wolf pack, Akela; Jack Reynor (‚ÄúTransformers: Age of Extinction‚Äù), as Mowgli‚Äôs brother Wolf; Eddie Marsan (TV‚Äôs ‚ÄúRay Donovan‚Äù), as Nisha‚Äôs mate, Vihaan; and Tom Hollander (‚ÄúBreathe‚Äù) as the scavenging hyena, Tabaqui.‚ÄúMowgli‚Äù is produced by Steve Kloves (‚ÄúFantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them‚Äù), Jonathan Cavendish (‚ÄúBreathe,‚Äù performance capture producer on ‚ÄúGodzilla‚Äù), and David Barron (the ‚ÄúHarry Potter‚Äù films), with Nikki Penny serving as executive producer.  The screenplay is by Kloves‚Äô daughter, Callie Kloves.  Serkis‚Äôs creative filmmaking team includes director of photography Michael Seresin (‚ÄúWar for the Planet of the Apes‚Äù), production designer Gary Freeman (‚ÄúTomb Raider‚Äù) and editors Mark Sanger (Oscar winner, ‚ÄúGravity‚Äù), Alex Marquez (‚ÄúSnowden‚Äù) and Jeremiah O‚ÄôDriscoll (‚ÄúFlight‚Äù).  The music is composed by Nitin Sawhney (‚ÄúBreathe‚Äù).--Follow #Mowgli on social media:http://www.mowglimovie.comhttp://facebook.com/MowgliMoviehttp://twitter.com/MowgliMoviehttp://instagram.com/MowgliMovie

description:
The mind is a set of cognitive faculties including consciousness, perception, thinking, and memory. It is usually defined as the faculty of an entity's thoughts and consciousness. It holds the power of imagination, recognition, and appreciation, and is responsible for processing feelings and emotions, resulting in attitudes and actions.

There is a lengthy tradition in philosophy, religion, psychology, and cognitive science about what constitutes a mind and what are its distinguishing properties.
In psychology, the word subconscious is the part of consciousness that is not currently in focal awareness. 

The human brain is the central organ of the human nervous system, and with the spinal cord makes up the central nervous system. The brain consists of the cerebrum, the brainstem and the cerebellum. It controls most of the activities of the body.

The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues which are socially relevant.The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son pushes Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

description:
Samantha about Rangamma Mangamma Song / Rangasthalam Third Single on Mythri Movie Makers. #Rangasthalam 2018 Telugu Movie ft. Ram Charan, Samantha and Aadhi Pinisetty. #Rangasthalam is Directed by Sukumar and Music composed by DSP / Devi Sri Prasad. Produced by Naveen Yerneni, Y Ravi Shankar and Mohan Cherukuri under Mythri Movie Makers banner. #RangasthalamThirdSingle #RangammaMangamma #RangasthalamOnMarch30th

Rangasthalam 3rd single Rangamma Mangamma will be out on March 8th at 6PM, on the occasion of Women's Day.

Samantha thanks audience for making Ranga Ranga Rangasthalana and Yentha Sakkagunave songs a great success.

Rangasthalam 2018 movie also ft. Anchor Anasuya, Jagapathi Babu, Gauthami among others. Pooja Hegde will be seen in a special song. 

#RamCharan #Samantha #Sukumar #PoojaHegde #SamanthaRuthPrabhu #AadhiPinisetty #DSP #DeviSriPrasad #Anasuya #JagapathiBabu

Here is something to know about Ram Charan's Family:

Ram Charan's paternal uncle Pawan Kalyan, was recently seen in Agnyaathavaasi Telugu movie, besides being active in Politics with his Janasena Party. Ram Charan's father, Tollywood's top actor, Chiranjeevi, has also played an important role in the AP Politics with his Prajarajyam party. Actor Chiranjeevi is now a member of the Congress. Ram Charan's wife Upasana Kamineni is the granddaughter of Dr.Pratap C Reddy, the founder and chairman of Apollo Hospitals.

Something to know about Samantha:
Samantha Akkineni (Samantha Ruth Prabhu), the female lead in Rangasthalam Telugu Movie recently tied the knot with Actor Akkineni Naga Chaitanya, the eldest son of Akkineni Nagarjuna. Samantha started her own NGO, Pratyusha Support, to provide medical support for women and children. She is the ambassador for Telangana Handlooms, having been appointed by the government of Telangana. 

Devi Sri Prasad, aka DSP, is one of the best music composers in Tollywood. He had recently worked for Nani's MCA: Middle Class Abbayi, Jr NTR's Jai Lava Kusa, Chiranjeevi's Khaidi No.150 and many more. The latest album to come from DSP after Rangasthalam is Mahesh Babu and Koratala Siva's upcoming film Bharat Ane Nenu.

Jagapathi Babu had earlier worked with Sukumar for NTR's Nannaku Prematho and garnered great applause for his performance. The Rangasthalam actor is also playing a vital role in Chiranjeevi's 151st film Sye Raa Narasimha Reddy.

The captain of the Rangasthalam, director Sukumar has given the top Tollywood actors a huge blockbuster. Nannaku Prematho with NTR, 1 Nenokkadine with Mahesh Babu, Arya with Allu Arjun and 100% love with Naga Chaitanya to name a few.

title: Barcelona vs Celta Vigo 2-2 - All Goals & Extended Highlights - La Liga 02/12/2017 HD
tags: Barcelona|"vs"|"Celta Vigo"|"2-2"|"Goals"|"Highlights"|"02"|"December"|"2017"|"Barcelona vs Celta Vigo"|"Barcelona vs Celta Vigo 2-2"|"Barcelona vs Celta Vigo 2017"|"Barcelona vs Celta Vigo all goals"|"Barcelona vs Celta Vigo highlights"|"Barcelona Highlights"|"Celta Vigo Highlights"|"La Liga"|"Messi"|"Suarez"|"Aspas"|"resumen goles"
description:
Barcelona vs Celta Vigo 2-2 - All Goals & Extended Highlights - La Liga 02/12/2017 HD
Goals: Iago Aspas 20', Lionel Messi 22', Luis Suarez 62', Gomez 70'.

Spanish La Liga
Barcelona vs Celta Vigo
12:00pm Saturday 2nd December
Camp Nou   (Att: 63208)

Maxi Gomez's equaliser secured Celta Vigo a 2-2 draw at Camp Nou, with Barcelona dropping points at home for the first time in a year.

Barcelona dropped points at home in LaLiga for the first time since December 2016 on Saturday, as Celta Vigo left Camp Nou with a battling 2-2 draw thanks to Maxi Gomez's equaliser.

Ernesto Valverde's men looked good value for all three points when Luis Suarez put them 2-1 up just after the hour mark, but Gomez struck soon after to ensure Barca drew a second successive league match following the 1-1 stalemate with Valencia last time out.

Iago Aspas gave Celta the lead, punishing Barca's slow start by rounding off an electric counter-attack with an easy finish, but that only seemed to jolt the home side into life.

Lionel Messi restored parity soon after with a clever finish, before then also hitting the post as Barca took charge.

Barca had to wait to take full advantage of their superiority again, but they did eventually go ahead just after the hour mark, with Suarez rounding off a fine move to become one of the 10 leading scorers in the club's history.

Gomez drew Celta level, though, and ultimately secured the visitors a point despite the home side's late pressure, giving the chasing pack hope of gaining on Barca at the top of the table this weekend.
